\b Rehan\b0\par
The folk of the plains, or Rehan are generally accepted as the original inhabitants of the island.  Their race's history stretches back into the times before the ancients, and while none of their cultural acheivements are ever considered revolutionary they are recognised for forming the first cognizant society on Lu'Tamohr.  While they bear no distinct racial characteristics, their history has led them to be extremely adaptable.\par
\par
They occupied the central plains of Lu'Tamohr and had no need for castles, walls and weapons. Thus they were completely suprised and overwhelmed by the Cvin invasion.\par
